{"id":"45c2aa26-f377-4d59-ac71-40ee16641d11","name":"Monsters Under Us","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 88, 255);\"><u>Welcome to the Federation</u></span></h1><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BeVXMCD48WqA6yRX3caUy.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Years ago, Earth suffered from an apocalyptic event, causing humanity to flee into space for survival.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">With 500 stations among the Sol System, humanity has managed to survive for a long time without Earth.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">However they are always trying to take back the planet from the destructive virus that holds the planet hostage.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 239, 255);\"><u>About the Humanity Galactic Federation (HGF)</u></span><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The HGF Control the Sol System in its entirety, spanning 500 stations among the entire system.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Led by their Supreme Leader, they have thrived. They have survived 210 Years in space thus far, with no sign of dwindling. The three biggest stations in the system are Station 347, 410, &amp; 001.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The capital of the HGF resides as Station 001, the seat of the Supreme Leader.</p><p></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 126, 255);\"><u>Important Personnel</u></span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 0, 255);\"><strong><em><u>Commander Fenra Sanders</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-QZ9eDT7GjjKnfVJnWUBZ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 76, 255);\"><strong><em><u>Chief HGF Enforcer Celene Hillfrost</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 76, 255);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZlvCnBSV-FiTIv20uHrSi.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 79, 79);\"><strong><em><u>Chief HGF Extractor Cyrus Striker</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/aI8iFqm7KJ5sVM4OqvtB1.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 231, 0);\"><strong><em><u>Supreme Leader Peter Énorme</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/U7EMpoHsel12pFAG4Er1_.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 113, 195);\"><strong><em><u>Fleet Commander Finn Indigo</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/817PcmgmlFvsGSL9i1orq.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 76, 240);\"><strong><em><u>Religious Leader of the Followers of Celestia Mienra Hall</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fqkZFHzrS_opYJvEmvGuD.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 169, 254);\"><strong><em><u>Religious Leader of Cosmology Eden Grace</u></em></strong></span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/k7PwuqIM4f98US1sWTtJ5.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"hj0NBec7a5jOhJWPntl8G.webp","creator":"JFlame861","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":82,"messages":896,"created_at":"2025-12-19T23:57:35.627545+00:00"}